OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FA crimefighting Cocker Spaniel called
OL,7,FGriffin has helped sniff out 13,000
OL,8,Fillegal cigarettes from a shop in
OL,9,FReading as part of a joint operation
OL,10,Fto crack down on illegal and
OL,11,Fcounterfeit cigarettes in the town.
OL,13,FTrading Standards officers from
OL,14,FReading Council, working with Thames
OL,15,FValley Police, impounded the haul of
OL,16,Fillegal tobacco products from Reading
OL,17,FMini Mart on Oxford Road earlier this
OL,18,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
