OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FThe operation was part of a National
OL,7,FTrading Standards initiative, in
OL,8,Fpartnership with HM Revenue and
OL,9,FCustoms, to tackle illegal tobacco,
OL,10,Fincluding cigarettes or hand rolling
OL,11,Ftobacco that have been smuggled,
OL,12,Fbootlegged or are counterfeit.
OL,14,FGriffin, handled by Stuart Phillips,
OL,15,Fbarked and wagged his tail excitedly
OL,16,Fas he located the concealed tobacco
OL,17,Fwithin a hidden compartment in a
OL,18,Fstorage area towards the back of the
OL,19,Fshop.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FDuring further searches of the
OL,7,Fpremises, a large shopping bag
OL,8,Fcontaining illegal tobacco was also
OL,9,Fidentified, believed to have been
OL,10,Fthrown onto the roof of the shop next
OL,11,Fdoor, in an attempt to evade detection.
OL,13,FIn total, more than 13,000 counterfeit
OL,14,Fcigarettes were seized as part of the
OL,15,Foperation and will now be destroyed.
OL,17,FThe total high street value of the
OL,18,Fseized items, had they been sold
OL,19,Fillegally, would have been around
OL,20,F#4,500.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FThe premises had been subject to a
OL,7,FClosure Notice served on 8 June 2026,
OL,8,Ffollowing concerns relating to ongoing
OL,9,Fcriminal behaviour linked to the sale
OL,10,Fof illicit tobacco.
OL,12,FAt Reading Magistrates' Court on 10
OL,13,FJune, a formal Closure Order was
OL,14,Fgranted, after evidence demonstrated
OL,15,Fcontinued unlawful trading despite
OL,16,Fprevious interventions by Trading
OL,17,FStandards.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FThe Court granted the Closure Order
OL,7,Funder the Anti-Social Behaviour, Crime
OL,8,Fand Policing Act 2014, enabling the
OL,9,FCouncil to close the premises for a
OL,10,Fperiod of up to three months to
OL,11,Fprevent further criminal activity and
OL,12,Fprotect the local community.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
