PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,FCllr Finn McGoldrick, Lead Member for
OL,7,FEnvironmental Services and Community
OL,8,FSafety, said: "This is another
OL,9,Fimpressive result in our wider
OL,10,Fcrackdown with partner agencies on
OL,11,Frogue traders who put profits before
OL,12,Fpublic safety; tackling organised
OL,13,Fcriminal activity in Reading and
OL,14,Fkeeping our residents safe.
OL,26,@pD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,F"I'd especially like to thank Griffin
OL,7,Fand his handler, Stuart. Detection
OL,8,Fdogs are highly skilled and can find
OL,9,Ftobacco and cigarettes hidden in the
OL,10,Fmost unlikely places. Offenders need
OL,11,Fto know that they will face
OL,12,Fconsequences if they choose to deal in
OL,13,Fthese illegal products. Hopefully, it
OL,14,Fwill also make traders think twice
OL,15,Fabout stocking these products.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,F"Far from being a victimless crime,
OL,7,Fthose involved in the illegal tobacco
OL,8,Ftrade make it easier for children to
OL,9,Fstart smoking, take advantage of cash-
OL,10,Fstrapped families, and help fund
OL,11,Forganised crime."
OL,13,FPolice Sergeant Alistair Mathieson, of
OL,14,Fthe Reading Neighbourhood Policing
OL,15,FTeam, said:"This was a great result
OL,16,Fthat underpins our lack of tolerance
OL,17,Ffor issues that impact the wellbeing
OL,18,Fof our communities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
