PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1781432282
OL,3,CWho's a good boy?! Canine crimefighter
OL,4,Csniffs out illegal cigarettes
OL,6,F"We are committed to working closely
OL,7,Fwith our partners to tackle this type
OL,8,Fof offending.
OL,10,F"The public also plays a vital role in
OL,11,Fhelping us tackle offending in our
OL,12,Fcommunities. If you have concerns
OL,13,Fabout illegal tobacco or related
OL,14,Fcriminality, please report it to us."
OL,16,FTo report sources of illegal tobacco,
OL,17,Fcontact the Illegal Tobacco Hotline on
OL,18,F0300 999 6 999, or via the website:
OL,19,Fhttps://www.stop- illegal-
OL,20,Ftobacco.co.uk/ where information can
OL,21,Fbe left anonymously.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@eO]
